| **`name`** | **`{prefix}-{semantic title}`** per [rule **50**](../../rules/50_mission-control-display-metadata-discipline.mdc) § *Lane title prefix conventions* (`PRD-`, `MP-`, `PH{N}-`, `PR{N}-`, `Pre-PR Review-` by skill role) — **not** generic placeholders such as "Child agent" alone |
