**PR review cycle (cyclic — post-create-pr)**

After **`create-pr`** opens a GitHub PR, **`coding-session`** owns a **repeatable review loop** until the PR merges or the developer defers. The Squad Leader **tracks** `pr-open` / `pr-review` phases via §8 host sync from **`coding-session`** re-emits — it does **not** run this loop.

```mermaid
